      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZARI EXACT (8) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in his excellent 19.32 win at this track over 340m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Rates on top and can find winning form again. LITTLE DAN (4) has a strong record here with eight wins and seven placings from 17 starts. Recorded a one length win (19.37) in a Free For All last time at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. SIMPLY DANGER (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 9 length eighth (26.52) but scored three back at this track (20.10). Has a good record here at this journey. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and four minor placings from nine starts. Likely to be thereabouts. KIWI ICE CUBE (3) placed last time out at this track and distance - worth considering.",
